text: DWFM (92.3 FM), broadcasting as FM Radio 92.3, is a radio station owned by Nation Broadcasting Corporation and operated by Philippine Collective Media Corporation It serves as the flagship station of the FM Radio Philippines network. The station's studio is located at 5th Floor, The Ignacia Place, 155 Mother Ignacia corner, Sgt. Esguerra Ave, Barangay South Triangle, Diliman, Quezon City; This station operates daily from 5:00 AM to 12:00 MN. Category:Radio stations in the Philippines
title: DWFM
